EXTRACTED VALUE: An unqualified success, and in my opinion, should be a must have for any Xbox 360 owner.
Forza 2 is a great game for novices and gearheads alike. Play it simple or fiddle with every last thing you can – the game works both ways.
Feels like Geometry Wars but with more great game modes, multiplayer and improved visuals.
With over 45 achievements to collect and never-ending fighting matches online, you will not run out of things to do in this game for a long time.
Personally co-op was one of my favorite aspects of GRAW1 and I was blown away with the amount of effort Ubisoft put into it this time around.
It's so pretty that it’s fun to just simply watch it rather than play it.
